name: marinated shrimp in avocado halves
instructions:
1. Dice shrimp and onions and place in medium-sized bowl.

2. Deseed and mince jalapeno and add to bowl.

3. Mince garlic, and add to bowl, along with cilantro leaves, tomato juice and lime juice.

4. Thoroughly mix together all ingredients. Refrigerate 30 minutes.

5. Just before serving, cut each avocado into halves and take out the pit.

6. Spoon marinated shrimp into the avocado halves and serve.
